              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 136 cm3 Ge(Li) detector. The efficiencies of",
                " two Ge(Li) detectors used in both places were",
                " calibrated using the same group of gamma-ray standard",
